BugHerd,is,a,visual,bug,tracking,and,project,management,app,built,for,web,developers,and,designers,It,lets,you,report,issues,directly,on,a,website,with,a,simple,point,and,click,BugHerd,automatically,grabs,all,browser,data,and,even,takes,screenshots,for,you,making,it,ideal,for,working,with,remote,teams,clients,and,QA,testers,The,BugHerd,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,and,functionality,of,BugHerd,Some,example,API,methods,include,listing,creating,and,managing,projects,listing,users,listing,and,creating,comments,and,listing,creating,and,managing,tasks